Package: bosc
Type: Package
Title: Behavioral Oscillation Scores and Phase Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bradley", "Buchsbaum", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com")
    )
Description: Implements behavioral oscillation scoring, surrogate testing,
    phase analysis, pairwise phase consistency (PPC) metrics, clustering, and
    plotting for behavioral and neural time series. Core methods follow Ter Wal
    et al. (2021) and the behavioral-oscillations reference software, with
    grouped trial-level and subject-level spectral and time-frequency workflows
    for dense behavioral sampling. See Ter Wal et al. (2021)
    <doi:10.1038/s41467-021-27323-3>.
License: CC BY 4.0 + file LICENSE
URL: https://bbuchsbaum.github.io/bosc/, https://github.com/bbuchsbaum/bosc
